{"tid":2508782,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知JB依個PR收咗中共幾多錢","createTime":"2021-04-29T04:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T09:14:48.000Z","uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"48233a6d4bd66c67ea276792e936ff8c08f37876","tid":2508782,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:16:55.000Z","msg":"夠膽Diss viutv藝人 神枱級組合error入面嘅何啟華一哥<br />\n係人都知我哋香港人唔可以批評viu半句壞話<br />\n就算真唔真都唔提得<br />\n條友仲唔係收咗tvb錢做PR？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DP3UKlfratw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDP3UKlfratw&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=a5b70bed\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DP3UKlfratw</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Wzj5vp9xm5c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWzj5vp9xm5c&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=6f3240df\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Wzj5vp9xm5c</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\">------------------分隔線--------------------</p><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">我知實有人又話我開po洗底<br />\n所以喺到講定先<br />\n無可否認我個po個題係開得衰<br />\n但我內文全部cm都係話佢好笑 <br />\n完全唔係惡意批評 你哋可以入去睇返<br />\n193係搞笑藝人 請問點解我話佢好笑都唔俾？<br />\n點解可以憑住幾張cap圖加自己片面之詞就話自己證據確鑿？<br />\n仲衰撚過中共啲莫須有<br />\n到我依家開po都俾人狙擊係五毛PR<br />\n連登仔係咪淨係識睇標題做人又唔識FC？<br />\n可唔可以自己俾小小判斷力？<br />\n<br />\n唔知咩事嘅可以入去睇返依兩個po<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>點解193唱歌可以咁難聽<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/hbfwBS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/hbfwBS</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有個痴線佬開po話我精神分裂+PR+有分身<br />\n<blockquote>證據確鑿！ PR 精神分裂。分化Error &amp; Mirror<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aNweMCU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aNweMCU</a></blockquote><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"4c6d6757b81006ba4435dde6fcdb1b2a1eaaa450","tid":2508782,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:47:50.000Z","msg":"咁多tvb打手負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連登淪陷喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd06b8fdfad2b81b6c989689be359e4532278d8","tid":2508782,"uid":373586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:49:27.000Z","msg":"柒咗咪認<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞咁多做乜撚"},{"pid":"a2e44a4f292c51723a75d163a4fc743cc2ca077e","tid":2508782,"uid":197716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:02:44.000Z","msg":"一哥串JB先"},{"pid":"2a46f0403cd336be36a482e72b46e8cd1383953a","tid":2508782,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2e44a4f292c51723a75d163a4fc743cc2ca077e","tid":2508782,"uid":197716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:02:44.000Z","msg":"一哥串JB先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:14:48.000Z","msg":"當時唔diss？隔幾年先出嚟搏乜？"}]}